maps.label: Mutations
maps.description: This visualization combines multiple mutation data types, including TCGA MutSig CV data produced by Firehose

maps.label: Welcome to GeneSpot
maps.description: This application allows users to view a variety of interactive visualizations of TCGA data.  Each particular 'open' button will activate the specified analysis.

views.label: Overview
views.text: This tool provides a way to view TCGA data from a gene-centric point-of-view. It includes a number of interactive visualizations, and allows the user to save their current exploration. This application also enables the user to select specific tumor types and genes of interest, and load data that is generated from a variety of TCGA analysis.
